data.description: Have you been searching for a home that offers a gourmet kitchen open to a huge family room that has breathtaking views of conservation and wildlife? Well look no more...M/I Homes is pleased to offer our newest home designs in the perfect area Connerton Village! Take advantage of resort style living with the incredible amenity center and thousands of acres of wildlife preserve with walking trails! Pictures are of the furnished model and for representation purposes only. Brokered And Advertised By: M/I HOMES Listing Agent: MARSHALL GRAY
